  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "03sBd+mXVxkMfnu+0MxAhCng1RQ=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# usePHToast replaces direct toast library imports in editors\n\nNever import `ToastContainer` or any toast library directly in editors or apps. The host app (Connect) already provides the toast infrastructure.\n\n```typescript\nimport { usePHToast } from \"@powerhousedao/reactor-browser\";\n\nexport default function Editor() {\n  const toast = usePHToast();\n\n  const handleSave = () => {\n    toast(\"Document saved!\", { type: \"success\" });\n  };\n}\n```\n\nAvailable toast types: `default`, `success`, `error`, `warning`, `info`, `connect-success`, `connect-warning`, `connect-loading`, `connect-deleted`.\n\nOptions include `autoClose` (ms or false) and `containerId` for targeting specific containers.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[editor patterns]]\n- [[gotchas]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:47.000Z"
    }
  },
